lines.text: You fool! Any last words before you die?
[coughs up blood]
It's been so long, since I snapped someone's neck.

[after knocking out several fighters]
That's Krillin with two L's and I do accept personal checks.
[kicks another fighter off the stage]
Go Gohan! Beat 'em all! You can do it!
Wha? Gohan's fighting? But he's a Super Saiyan! That's not fair! Huh?
Haaa!
[four fighters fly off the stage]
Piccolo too? Where's Trunks? Make it a full set.
[10 fighters fall behind him, Krillin looks down and smirks]
Me and my big mouth, this is now officially unfair.

[about to fight Piccolo]
I can do this, he's not unbeatable. Well unless he uses his Special Beam Cannon, then I'm dead.
I know your kind, you think you can just walk in and take our planet.
[energy crackles around him]
Gohan, I love you sweetie!

[embarrassed]
Mom, not so loud!
You own this, Trunks! Get 'em, and then we can go on vacation!

[to himself, embarrassed]
Tactful as always, Mother.
Krillin, don't get yourself killed!

[to himself, annoyed]
Oh, I'll survive. Then, it's bacon time.
Bojack, you will *not* take this planet! Hya!
[Trunks fires a energy beam]

[Kogu, who is sitting in a tree unknowingly to Trunks, shoots a energy blast at him]
Watch where you point that thing, I might get the wrong idea! We may be fighting, but this is still a tournament! No killing allowed!
[Kogu jumps down from the tree and throws a punch, Trunks dodges it, he then tries to punch Kogu, but Kogu blocks it, he then throws Trunks]
Whoa! what the hell are you?
[Koju kicks Trunks, but Trunks dodges it, and kicks Koju back, Trunks then gives Koju a knee kick but Koju blacks it with his sword]
Someone not to be trifled with, boy!
Master Bojack has no equal!
